Animoto is bringing sexy back. With this release we ve made some design improvements that will make this app really really ridiculously good looking. We could ve stopped there. And it would have been an awesome release. 5 minutes later But we didn t! Our team went on a vision quest and we traveled the world for inspiration. We wanted to deliver something extra special for our Marketing Video Builder Customers. We studied thousands of years of ancient history to figure out how people have historically gotten an item from point a to point b. We explored everything from the Pony Express in the mid 1800 s to Drone Delivery experiments today! That s when we realized our users were plugging their phones into their computers downloading their photos videos and then hopefully uploading the correct files to their Marketing Video projects on the web. This sounded worse than the Pony Express to us. We re not promising to deliver photos videos via Drone yet BUT with this update our Marketing Video Builder Customers will now have the superpower of uploading photos videos from their phone DIRECTLY into their existing Marketing Video Builder Projects on the web! Welcome to version 9.0 people! It ll only get better from here. Plus lots of pesky bugs have been squashed in this release along with improvements to overall app stability. Love Animoto Please review our app in the App Store. If you have any issues with the app please email us at help animoto.com.

You know the feeling of being interrupted while you are doing something Then you go back to whatever it was that you were doing later on but you can t remember where you left off! Was I adding chocolate syrup to my ice cream sundae Or was it whipped cream! We hate that feeling at Animoto too!! Now your in progress projects remember exactly where you were in the process. We ve also added overflow controls in the video list! You know those buttons that look like meatballs You can now share copy or delete videos you ve created right from the video list screen. If you hate unnecessary steps you re going to love this update. If you love unnecessary steps you ll still love this update too just not as much. Last but not least with this release you can now see but not edit YET the in progress projects you ve been working on from the web! Plus lots of pesky bugs have been squashed in this release along with improvements to overall app stability. Love Animoto Please review our app in the App Store. If you have any issues with the app please email us at help animoto.com.

After our last release we really put our app under the microscope and found a few things that weren t quite right. Turns out they were microbes. So we took the app back out from under the microscope which made it a lot easier to use! and found a couple bugs to fix. Enjoy making great videos with even fewer bugs in this release and let us know if you want to buy a gently used microscope.

At Animoto we sweat the details. A lot. No seriously we re buying deodorant in bulk. They say success is 10 inspiration and 90 perspiration. We may have pushed it up to 95 . Enjoy fewer bugs and more stability in this release. We ll just be over here getting rehydrated.
